up-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Integrasi WhatsApp</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-sm\">Broadcast pengumuman, pengingat iuran, dan update laporan langsung ke WhatsApp warga.</p></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent text-secondary-foreground bg-white/50 hover:bg-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0 h-5 border-0 shadow-sm\">Starter</div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent text-secondary-foreground bg-white/50 hover:bg-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0 h-5 border-0 shadow-sm\">Pro</div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent text-secondary-foreground bg-white/50 hover:bg-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0 h-5 border-0 shadow-sm\">Business</div></div><div class=\"flex items-center text-primary font-medium text-sm opacity-0 -translate-x-2 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all duration-300\">Lihat Detail <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 bg-green-100/30 dark:bg-green-900/20\"></div></div></div></a></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><a class=\"block h-full\" href=\"/features/portal-umkm\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-car