UMKM</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-sm\">Dukung ekonomi warga dengan marketplace khusus untuk UMKM di lingkungan Anda.</p></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent text-secondary-foreground bg-white/50 hover:bg-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0 h-5 border-0 shadow-sm\">Business</div></div><div class=\"flex items-center text-primary font-medium text-sm opacity-0 -translate-x-2 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all duration-300\">Lihat Detail <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 bg-yellow-100/30 dark:bg-yellow-900/20\"></div></div></div></a></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><a class=\"block h-full\" href=\"/features/auto-payout\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground h-full border-none shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden bg-indigo-100/50 dark:bg-indigo-900/20\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-background/60 backdrop-blur-[2px] flex items-center justify-center z-20 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"><span class=\"font-bold text-sm bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-lg transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300\">Segera Hadir</span></div><div class=\"p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col h-full relative z-10\"><div class=\"mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-white shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wallet w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M19 7V4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h15a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4h-3a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h3a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-2a1 1 0 0 0-1-1\"></path><path d=\"M3 5v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h15a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-4\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full py-0.5 font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 text-foreground bg-background/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-0 text-[10px] px-2 h-5\">Soon</div></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-2xl mb-3 tracking-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Auto Payout</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-sm\">Pencairan dana iuran otomatis ke rekening pengurus secara berkala dan aman.</p></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent text-secondary-foreground bg-white/50 hover:bg-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0 h-5 border-0 shadow-sm\">Pro</div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent text-secondary-foreground bg-white/50 hover:bg-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0 h-5 border-0 shadow-sm\">Business</div></div><div class=\"flex items-center text-primary font-medium text-sm opacity-0 -translate-x-2 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all duration-300\">Lihat Detail <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 bg-indigo-100/30 dark:bg-indigo-900/20\"></div></div></div></a></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><a class=\"block h-full\" href=\"/features/produk-digital-ppob\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground h-full border-none shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden bg-cyan-100/50 dark:bg-cyan-900/20\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-background/60 backdrop-blur-[2px] flex items-center justify-center z-20 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"><span class=\"font-bold text-sm bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-lg transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300\">Segera Hadir</span></div><div class=\"p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col h-full relative z-10\"><div class=\"mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-white shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full py-0.5 font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 text-foreground bg-background/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-0 text-[10px] px-2 h-5\">Soon</div></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-2xl mb-3 tracking-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Produk Digital PPOB</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-sm\">Beli pulsa, token listrik, dan bayar tagihan langsung dari aplikasi warga.</p></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent text-secondary-foreground bg-white/50 hover:bg-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0 h-5 border-0 shadow-sm\">Pro</div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent text-secondary-foreground bg-white/50 hover:bg-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0 h-5 border-0 shadow-sm\">Business</div></div><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground italic mb-4\">*Komisi hanya di Business</p><div class=\"flex items-center text-primary font-medium text-sm opacity-0 -translate-x-2 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all duration-300\">Lihat Detail <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 bg-cyan-100/30 dark:bg-cyan-900/20\"></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 container\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-primary px-6 py-16 md:px-12 md:py-24 text-center text-primary-foreground shadow-2xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent mb-6 bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 text-white border-none px-4 py-1 text-sm backdrop-blur-sm\">KEAMANAN &amp; PRIVASI</div><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight\">Standar Keamanan Kelas Dunia</h2><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Kami menjaga integritas data dan transaksi Anda dengan infrastruktur berlisensi serta teknologi enkripsi terkini.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-start justify-center gap-12 md:gap-8\"><div class=\"text-white max-w-[350px] flex flex-col items-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative w-[200px] h-[96px] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105\"><img alt=\"Terdaftar Resmi di Komdigi\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"96\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fpse.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fpse.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fpse.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"text-lg px-2 md:px-4 text-balance text-white font-medium\">Terdaftar Resmi di Komdigi</p></div><div class=\"text-white max-w-[350px] flex flex-col items-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative w-[200px] h-[96px] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105\"><img alt=\"Enkripsi Data Tingkat Tinggi (AES-256)\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"96\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Faes.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Faes.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Faes.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"text-lg px-2 md:px-4 text-balance text-white font-medium\">Enkripsi Data Tingkat Tinggi (AES-256)</p></div><div class=\"text-white max-w-[350px] flex flex-col items-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative w-[200px] h-[96px] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105\"><img alt=\"Proteksi Koneksi SSL/TLS Global\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"96\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fssl.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fssl.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fssl.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"text-lg px-2 md:px-4 text-balance text-white font-medium\">Proteksi Koneksi SSL/TLS Global</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 border-b bg-muted/10\"><div class=\"container\"><p class=\"text-center text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-muted-foreground mb-8 tracking-[0.2em]\">OFFICIAL PARTNERS</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-12 md:gap-20\"><div class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors cursor-default\">Google Cloud</div><div class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors cursor-default\">AWS</div><div class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors cursor-default\">flip</div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 bg-background overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/80 mb-4\">Testimoni Warga</div><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4\">Apa Kata Pengguna Sahabat Warga</h2><p class=\"text-muted-foreground text-lg\">Dipercaya oleh komunitas dan pengembang di seluruh Indonesia.</p></div><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex gap-8 w-max\"><div class=\"w-[350px] md:w-[400px] flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"p-6 pt-6 space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed italic\">“<!-- -->Iuran dan laporan keuangan jadi rapi. Warga bisa lihat transaksi secara real-time.<!-- -->”</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold\">B</div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">Budi Santoso</p><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Pengurus RT, Jakarta</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-[350px] md:w-[400px] flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"p-6 pt-6 space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed italic\">“<!-- -->Komunikasi warga lebih cepat, dan data penghuni lebih tertata dengan baik.<!-- -->”</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold\">D</div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">Dewi Lestari</p><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Pengembang Perumahan, Bekasi</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-[350px] md:w-[400px] flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"p-6 pt-6 space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed italic\">“<!-- -->Bayar iuran jadi mudah, notifikasi jelas, dan tidak perlu lagi catatan manual.<!-- -->”</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold\">R</div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">Rizky Pratama</p><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Warga, Surabaya</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-[350px] md:w-[400px] flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"p-6 pt-6 space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed italic\">“<!-- -->Aplikasi ini sangat membantu transparansi dana warga. Sangat direkomendasikan!<!-- -->”</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold\">A</div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">Andi Wijaya</p><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Ketua RW, Bandung</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-[350px] md:w-[400px] flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"p-6 pt-6 space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed italic\">“<!-- -->Fitur surat pengantarnya sangat praktis, tidak perlu bolak-balik ke rumah RT.<!-- -->”</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-